{"tid":1497131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"210個Youtube假消息頻道被刪","createTime":"2019-08-22T23:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T09:49:40.000Z","uid":34160,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"febf495bc04a2a55c0db7e043bb13dc7795115e0","tid":1497131,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:29:51.000Z","msg":"When identifying and preventing threats, we exchange information with industry partners and law enforcement, and also apply our own internal investigative tools as well as intelligence from third parties.<br />\n<br />\nEarlier this week, as part of our ongoing efforts to combat coordinated influence operations, we disabled 210 channels on YouTube when we discovered channels in this network behaved in a coordinated manner while uploading videos related to the ongoing protests in Hong Kong. This discovery was consistent with recent observations and actions related to China announced by Facebook and Twitter.<br />\n<br />\nWe found use of VPNs and other methods to disguise the origin of these accounts and other activity commonly associated with coordinated influence operations.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.blog.google/outreach-initiatives/public-policy/maintaining-integrity-our-platforms/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blog.google%2Foutreach-initiatives%2Fpublic-policy%2Fmaintaining-integrity-our-platforms%2F&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1dqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=507931f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.blog.google/outreach-initiatives/public-policy/maintaining-integrity-our-platforms/</a>"},{"pid":"9f1a5bbf0fa182e5ef6d29be653d2483c1532940","tid":1497131,"uid":281926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:09:26.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><